{"tid":1108001,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國金融大亨爆料墨西哥毒梟以每人5萬美元報酬「走私」中國特工入美國","createTime":"2019-04-15T15:44:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-15T17:48:57.000Z","uid":28765,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"60ade0fc5c47f7609ff8a619c06c093c251c0d97","tid":1108001,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T15:44:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/business/page/800/2019/04/15/phpQj7OC2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fbusiness%2Fpage%2F800%2F2019%2F04%2F15%2FphpQj7OC2.jpg&h=f0db3cd5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國知名對沖基金大佬巴斯（Kyle Bass）。（彭博）<br />\n<br />\n〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕曾在2008年金融海嘯精準做空次貸而一戰成名的海曼資本管理公司（Hayman Capital Management）創始人、知名美國對沖基金大佬巴斯（Kyle Bass）13日在推特上爆料，墨西哥販毒集團在德州邊境以每人5萬美元的價格，將中國特工走私至美國，呼籲美國應在邊境實施新政策，以防範中國滲透。<br />\n<br />\n巴斯13日在推特上表示：「墨西哥販毒集團以每人5萬美元的價格，在德州邊境將中國特工走私至美國，集團表示，這比毒品走私更有利可圖。美國需要立即在邊境實施1項新政策，特別是針對中國的擔憂」。<br />\n<br />\n巴斯補充道，他與作為「鐵桿民主黨」的太太在上個週末從空中、陸地與海面上遊覽了整個美墨邊境，他認為此事「不是黨派問題，而是國家安全問題」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2759599\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2759599&d=BdEUjZUsFG%2BHnlCy9NhCd63e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=ace988c6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2759599&h=c8ae976a\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/2759599</a>"},{"pid":"06b10d73a5083d6f98b22e395c38b163b2544022","tid":1108001,"uid":21545,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T15:50:43.000Z","msg":"世界兩個最大黑社會合作<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77223fb6f2f8a84c87696fbe00b44a83396397c7","tid":1108001,"uid":76310,"like":1,"dislike":16,"score":-15,"quote":{"pid":"06b10d73a5083d6f98b22e395c38b163b2544022","tid":1108001,"uid":21545,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T15:50:43